snippet.title: StarGazing - An astronomically relaxing pattern puzzler - Out Now Announcement
snippet.description:
iOS/Apple App Store: https://apps.apple.com/py/app/stargazing-by-whitepot/id1491340912?l=en
Android/Google Play Store: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.WhitepotStudios.StarGazing

StarGazing by Whitepot Studios is an astronomically relaxing, beautiful, starry-eyed pattern-puzzler, available RIGHT NOW free-to-play on iOS and Android with our first batch of 51 constellations for you to enjoy.
